il.technion.ewolf.kbr.concurrent

クラス FutureCallback<T,A>

  • java.lang.Object
    • il.technion.ewolf.kbr.concurrent.FutureCallback<T,A>
  • 型パラメータ:
    T - the result type
    A - any arbitrary attachment
    すべての実装されたインタフェース:
    CompletionHandler<T,A>, java.util.concurrent.Future<T>

    public class FutureCallback<T,A>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.concurrent.Future<T>, CompletionHandler<T,A>
    Convert a CompletionHandler into a future. the get method simply blocks until the callback was called
